.
 The matrix form of Eq.
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:I1I2"

\end_inset

 is then
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A_{jk}I^{(k)}=\boldsymbol{q}
\]

\end_inset

where the elements of the stiffness matrix 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 are
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
A_{jk} & =\left(1-\frac{inS_{\Omega k}}{2}\frac{B_{0(\ph)}}{\Delta\psi}\right)\delta_{(j-1)k}+\left(-1-\frac{inS_{\Omega k}}{2}\frac{B_{0(\ph)}}{\Delta\psi}\right)\delta_{jk},
\end{align}

\end_inset

and the 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

th entry of vector 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{q}$
\end_inset

