\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In harmonics in 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi$
\end_inset

 this becomes
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\boldsymbol{B}\cdot\nabla_{RZ}p_{n}+inB^{\varphi}p_{n} & =s_{n}\,.
