If we take no toroidicity and harmonic RHS term with poloidal harmonic 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 we obtain
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
i(mB^{\vartheta}+nB^{\varphi})p_{mn} & =s_{mn}\\
p_{mn} & =\frac{s_{mn}}{i(mB^{\vartheta}+nB^{\varphi})}\,.
\end{align*}

